\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2421:\"<div class=\"KonaBody\"><p>I uploaded v1.9.8 and 1.9.8.1 of Top 10 plugin for WordPress. If you&#8217;re an existing user, you&#8217;ll be able to upgrade the plugin from within your WordPress Admin interface itself.</p>\n<p>Changes in this version include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Custom post support. Choose which custom post types to display in the top posts</li>\n<li>New: More display options. Select which archives you want to display the post count</li>\n<li>New: Option to open links in new window</li>\n<li>New: Option to add nofollow attribute to links</li>\n<li>New: Option to exclude posts by ID in the list of top posts being displayed</li>\n<li>New: Option to prevent display of the Visit Count on posts by ID</li>\n<li>New: Option to choose between using CSS styles or HTML attributes for thumbnail width and height. <em>HTML width and height attributes are default</em></li>\n<li>New: Option to restrict the title to fixed number of characters</li>\n<li>New: Option to add the date to the list</li>\n<li>Modified: Numbers are now formatted based on the locale</li>\n<li>Fixed: Plugin will now create thumbnails from the first image in gallery custom posts</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://i1.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/New-in-Top-10-v1.9.8.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-3542\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3542\" alt=\"New in Top 10 v1.9.8\" src=\"http://i1.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/New-in-Top-10-v1.9.8.png?resize=620%2C436\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you haven&#8217;t heard of this plugin yet, <a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/top-10/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Top 10</a> will count the number of page views on your single posts on a daily as well as overall basis. You can then display the page view count on individual posts and pages as well as display a list of most popular posts based on page views. Includes a sidebar widget to display the popular posts. And, all settings can be configured from within your WordPress Admin area itself!</p>\n<p class=\"downloads\"><a href=\"http://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/top-10.zip\">Download Top 10 v1.9.8.1</a></p>\n</div><hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/08/16/top-10-v1-9-8/\">Top 10 v1.9.8</a> was first posted on August 16, 2013 at 11:45 pm.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/08/16/top-10-v1-9-8/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"TwitterCounter v1.6.1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/07/21/twittercounter-v1-6-1/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/07/21/twittercounter-v1-6-1/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 21 Jul 2013 21:35:50 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"twitter\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"TwitterCounter\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/?p=3535\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:673:\"I&#8217;ve pushed through a minor update of my TwitterCounter WordPress plugin. TwitterCounter plugin allows you to integrate TwitterCounter.com buttons on your blog. Additionally, you can add the Twitter Widget to your blog, which shows which twitter users recently visited your blog or website. Manually add where you would like to display the badge / remote [&#8230;]<hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/07/21/twittercounter-v1-6-1/\">TwitterCounter v1.6.1</a> was first posted on July 21, 2013 at 10:35 pm.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Ajay D\\&#039;Souza\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1573:\"<div class=\"KonaBody\"><p>I&#8217;ve pushed through a minor update of my <a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/twittercounter/\">TwitterCounter WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-3515 alignright\" alt=\"WordPress Plugin Add to All\" src=\"http://i2.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/wordpress-logo-notext-bg1.png?resize=111%2C111\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>TwitterCounter plugin allows you to integrate <a href=\"http://twittercounter.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TwitterCounter.com</a> buttons on your blog.</p>\n<p>Additionally, you can add the Twitter Widget to your blog, which shows which twitter users recently visited your blog or website. Manually add where you would like to display the badge / remote or use the WordPress sidebar widgets instead.</p>\n<p>This release fixes a <a href=\"http://techtites.com/2013/how-to-prevent-csrf-vulnerability-in-wordpress-plugins-and-themes/\">potential CSRF vulnerability</a> and also includes fixes for PHP in strict mode.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re already using TwitterCounter on your blog, then you can upgrade the plugin from within your WordPress interface itself. New users can get hold of the plugin <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/twittercounter/\">here</a>.</p>\n</div><hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/07/21/twittercounter-v1-6-1/\">TwitterCounter v1.6.1</a> was first posted on July 21, 2013 at 10:35 pm.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/07/21/twittercounter-v1-6-1/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"Top 10 v1.9.7 and 100,000 downloads\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/07/04/top-10-v1-9-7-and-100000-downloads/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/07/04/top-10-v1-9-7-and-100000-downloads/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 04 Jul 2013 19:19:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"top-10\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/?p=3525\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:637:\"Released a tiny update to Top 10 a few days back in an attempt to find a solution to the tracking issue that was introduced in v1.9.5. Users now have an option to turn on jQuery to track plugin visits. You&#8217;ll find that as &#8220;W3 Total Cache fix&#8221;. And, last week Top 10 crossed 100,000 [&#8230;]<hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/07/04/top-10-v1-9-7-and-100000-downloads/\">Top 10 v1.9.7 and 100,000 downloads</a> was first posted on July 4, 2013 at 8:19 pm.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Ajay D\\&#039;Souza\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1661:\"<div class=\"KonaBody\"><p>Released a tiny update to Top 10 a few days back in an attempt to find a solution to the tracking issue that was introduced in v1.9.5.</p>\n<p>Users now have an option to turn on jQuery to track plugin visits. You&#8217;ll find that as &#8220;W3 Total Cache fix&#8221;.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://i0.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Top-10-v1.9.7-General-options.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3527\" alt=\"Top 10 v1.9.7 - General options\" src=\"http://i1.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Top-10-v1.9.7-General-options.png?resize=229%2C300\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a></p>\n<p>And, last week Top 10 crossed 100,000 downloads. Am glad this plugin has received such good acceptance and I thank all of the users of this plugin for this!</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;ve been using Top 10, why not give it a <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/top-10\">5-star review</a>. If you&#8217;re facing issues do use the <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/top-10\">support forums</a> since it is one centralised place that I can easily monitor.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3526\" alt=\"Top 10 - 100k downloads\" src=\"http://i2.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Top-10-100k.png?resize=183%2C91\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n</div><hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/07/04/top-10-v1-9-7-and-100000-downloads/\">Top 10 v1.9.7 and 100,000 downloads</a> was first posted on July 4, 2013 at 8:19 pm.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/07/04/top-10-v1-9-7-and-100000-downloads/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Top 10 v1.9.6\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/06/16/top-10-v1-9-6/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/06/16/top-10-v1-9-6/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 16 Jun 2013 09:46:32 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"top-10\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/?p=3520\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:613:\"Update: v1.9.6 still has bugs on some installs where the Ajax is not run and counts are not incremented. I pushed through relatively minor updates to Top 10. The main reason for this update was to get the plugin working better with W3 Total Cache where counts weren&#8217;t updated due to its aggressive caching. The [&#8230;]<hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/06/16/top-10-v1-9-6/\">Top 10 v1.9.6</a> was first posted on June 16, 2013 at 10:46 am.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Ajay D\\&#039;Souza\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2023:\"<div class=\"KonaBody\"><p><strong>Update: v1.9.6 still has bugs on some installs where the Ajax is not run and counts are not incremented.</strong></p>\n<p>I pushed through relatively minor updates to Top 10. The main reason for this update was to get the plugin working better with W3 Total Cache where counts weren&#8217;t updated due to its aggressive caching.</p>\n<p>The title of the posts also have their very own title tag which allows you to separately style this. And, lastly, users can now turn on or off the counting for overall and / or daily posts. So, if you don&#8217;t need the daily counter, you&#8217;ll get some performance improvements. v1.9.6 fixes bugs introduced in v1.9.5 where the daily counter remained off permanently.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3521\" alt=\"Top 10 v1.9.6\" src=\"http://i0.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Top-10-v1.9.6.png?resize=496%2C180\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>As usual, if you&#8217;re seeking support on the plugin check out the <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/top-10\">support forum</a> first. And, if you&#8217;ve been using this plugin a lot, do consider giving a <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/top-10\">5 star review</a>.</p>\n<h3>Changes in 1.9.5 and 1.9.6</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>New: CSS class <code>tptn_title</code> that can be used to style the title of the posts</li>\n<li>New: Option to disable Daily or Overall counters</li>\n<li>Fixed: Counter to work with different directory structures. <em>Thanks Nathan for the fix</em></li>\n<li>Fixed: To make it work with W3 Total Cache. <em>Thanks Angelo for the fix</em></li>\n<li>Modified: timthumb will now work if you have JetPack Proton activated</li>\n</ul>\n</div><hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/06/16/top-10-v1-9-6/\">Top 10 v1.9.6</a> was first posted on June 16, 2013 at 10:46 am.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/06/16/top-10-v1-9-6/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Contextual Related Posts v1.8.8\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/06/02/contextual-related-posts-v1-8-8/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/06/02/contextual-related-posts-v1-8-8/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 02 Jun 2013 11:50:38 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"related posts\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/?p=3165\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:650:\"I uploaded v1.8.8 of Contextual Related Posts to the WordPress.org repository. This is a minor update that add two new features: New: Clear cache button New: Option to add the date before the post title If you have any questions / bug reports, please post them in the WordPress support forums. I check these regularly. [&#8230;]<hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/06/02/contextual-related-posts-v1-8-8/\">Contextual Related Posts v1.8.8</a> was first posted on June 2, 2013 at 12:50 pm.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Ajay D\\&#039;Souza\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1591:\"<div class=\"KonaBody\"><p>I uploaded v1.8.8 of <a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/contextual-related-posts/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Contextual Related Posts</a> to the WordPress.org repository. This is a minor update that add two new features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Clear cache button</li>\n<li>New: Option to add the date before the post title</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3166\" alt=\"Contextual Related Posts - Clear Cache\" src=\"http://i0.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Contextual-Related-Posts-Clear-Cache.png?resize=620%2C95\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>If you have any questions / bug reports, please post them in the WordPress <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contextual-related-posts\">support forums</a>. I check these regularly. And, while you’re around there, why not <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/contextual-related-posts\">write a good review</a> for the plugin?</p>\n<div class=\"downloads\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contextual-related-posts.zip\">Download Contextual Related Posts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/contextual-related-posts/\">Visit Contextual Related Posts plugin page</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div><hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/06/02/contextual-related-posts-v1-8-8/\">Contextual Related Posts v1.8.8</a> was first 